718452f-a.title: Manhattan: Central Park West - 67th Street
718452f-a.text:
Central Park West, west side, from 67th Street. In the center, demolition work is about to begin on the Town House apartments. It was listed as 71-75 CPW and also known as Chatham Court. Beyond it, on the S.W. corner of 68th Street, may be seen the Second Church of Christ Scientist.
In the foreground, the sidewalk and street has been torn up for construction work on the Eighth Avenue subway. September 24, 1928  F.L. Sparr
